    {
      "id": "55b80f7e-6d61-4a37-9e07-26b3f300ff31",
      "name": "Sticky Note 136c5d2b",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        100,
        300
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "content": {
          "config": {
            "name": "How to use",
            "position": [
              -64,
              208
            ],
            "parameters": {
              "content": "# Populate personality_prod row\n\nClick **Execute workflow** to upsert the `personality_prod` row in `cs_project_config` with 28 values extracted from the PE prod workflows.\n\n## Columns left blank (fill manually in the table UI if needed)\n- `ticket_custom_field_automation_label_id` — no `automationCustomFieldID` passed in any PE flow\n- `ticket_field_contact_form_classification_id` — PE Zendesk trigger doesn't include this field\n- `ticket_field_chatbot_classification_id` — no PE chatbot refunds workflow exists\n- `ticket_custom_status_chatbot_automated_id` — same reason\n- `macro_account_deletion_id` — PE main flow has no deletion-request branch\n- `category_value_cancellation_account_removal` — same reason\n- `refund_macro_rejection_alt_id` — only one rejection macro in PE\n- `refund_macro_monthly_legacy_id` — no legacy monthly in PE\n- `refund_value_monthly_alt`, `refund_value_30day_last_charge_alt` — no distinct alt strings in PE\n- `macro_thanks_reply_id`, `message_limit_threshold`, `macro_cancellation_confirmation`, `macro_refund_confirmation`, `macro_single_refund_complaint`, `macro_double_refund_complaint` — no PE 2nd-message workflow yet\n- `slack_dev_error_channel_id` — not applicable to a prod row\n\n## Note on auth\nPE prod currently uses Bearer token auth, but HMAC will be used going forward. `hmac_key_id` is populated as `perso-prod` per Antonio's instruction.\n\n## Pre-existing bugs in PE prod workflows (NOT fixed here, just flagged)\n- `PE prod - Zendesk tickets main automation flow` → `Set refund and cancellation vars`: `zendeskDomain=lovestylehelp` (LS leftover), should be `personalitytest`\n- `PE prod - Refund requests flow` → `Edit Fields11` (last_charge): `macroID=26043963752220` (LS macro), should be `35702528266653`\n- `PE prod - Refund requests flow` → `Edit Fields12` (two_charges): `macroID=26043989469084` (LS macro), should be `35702549088285`\n- `PE prod - Refund requests flow` → \"Reply to customer\" upsell nodes: `ticket.custom_fields.id=24285840352924` (LS category field), should be `21549590739229`\n- `PE prod - Zendesk tickets main automation flow` → `Rate limit tester` Code node contains a hardcoded Bearer token and `dev.lovestyle.co` URL. Appears unused but should be removed for security hygiene.\n\nThe templated versions reading from this table will use the CORRECT values regardless of the bugs above.\n\n## After running\nVerify the row in the data table view, then archive this workflow.",
              "height": 640,
              "width": 700,
              "color": 5
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
